# HOW TO GET YOUR RIOT API KEY

1. Go to: https://developer.riotgames.com/
2. Sign in with your Riot Games account
3. Click "REGISTER PRODUCT" or "Generate API Key"
4. Copy your Development API Key (starts with RGAPI-)
5. Create a file named "riot_api_key.txt" in this folder
6. Paste your key in the file (one line only)

Example format:
RGAPI-xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx

⚠️  IMPORTANT:
- Development keys expire after 24 hours
- You can generate a new one daily for free
- Never share your API key publicly
- The key is already in .gitignore for safety

Rate Limits (Free Tier):
- 20 requests per second
- 100 requests per 2 minutes
- Perfect for analyzing 50-100 games per champion
